    "content": "----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n                        Crash And Burn - Savage Garden\r\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nTabbed By: Dylan Johnson\r\ne-mail: always_atticus@hotmail.com\r\n\r\nTuning: Standard\r\n\r\nIntro/Verse 1/Pre-Chorus (NO BASS)\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus (1:11) 4x\r\nG|-------------------|\r\nD|-2~2~2222----------|\r\nA|----------2~2~0~0~-|\r\nE|-------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n(1:30 - 1:38) NO BASS\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 2 (1:39) 2x\r\nG|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-2222222222222222--------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------------2222222222222222-4444444444444444-0000000000000000-----|\r\nE|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Pre-Chorus (1:58) 1x (My way to play this part; it sounds cooler) 12's/14's\r\nG|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-2222222222222222-4444444444444444-7777777777777777-12-12-12--14-14-14---|\r\nA|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus (2:07) 4x\r\nG|-------------------|\r\nD|-2~2~2222----------|\r\nA|----------2~2~0~0~-|\r\nE|-------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Bridge (2:26) 1x\r\nG|----------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------|\r\nA|-44444444-0000-2222-44444444-0000-2-2-2-|\r\nE|----------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab](2:36) 2x\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-2222222222222222----------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------------2222222222222222-4444444444444444-0000000000000000-|\r\nE|---------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab](2:54) 2x\r\nG|----------------------|\r\nD|-2~-------------------|\r\nA|-------2~----4~----0~-|\r\nE|----------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab](3:15) Repeat until song ends\r\nG|-------------------|\r\nD|-2~2~2222----------|\r\nA|----------2~2~0~0~-|\r\nE|-------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nThere ya go! Simple as that! comments? corrections? greatly welcomed :D\r\n\r\n============================================================================\r\n| /  slide up\r\n| \\  slide down\r\n| h  hammer-on\r\n| p  pull-off\r\n| ~  ring out\r\n| +  harmonic\r\n| x  Mute note\r\n============================================================================",
